title: PVC/WPC profile extrusion line
short_description: The line of this model is adapted to the production of PVC and WPC type profiles. The extruder motor with a production capacity of up to 100 kg per hour has a power of 22 kW. The width of the manufactured product reaches a maximum of 240 mm.
short_description_uz: Ushbu modeldagi liniya PVC va WPC turdagi profillarni ishlab chiqarishga moslashgan. Liniya soatiga 100 kg gacha mahsulot ishlab chiqarish quvvatiga ega ekstruder motori esa 22 kW quvvatga ega. Ishlab chiqarilgan mahsulot eni maksimal 240 mm gacha yetadi.
short_description_ru: Линия данной модели адаптирована для производства профилей типа ПВХ и ДПК. Двигатель экструдера производительностью до 100 кг в час имеет мощность 22 кВт. Ширина выпускаемого изделия достигает максимум 240 мм.

long_description:
The line of this model is adapted to the production of PVC and WPC type profiles. The extruder motor with a production capacity of up to 100 kg per hour has a power of 22 kW. The width of the manufactured product reaches a maximum of 240 mm.

 

 

Basic parameters
Model US-SJZ55/110
Extruder motor 22 kW
Down-stream  machine YF240
Product width 240 mm
Capacity 100 kg/hr
